{"TopicId":222685,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Followers Gone","CreatedByName":"Kerbalsaurus","CreatedById":222386,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-06T14:57:10Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Kerbalsaurus","CreatedById":222386,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-06T14:57:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI clicked on my profile to find out that every follower I have is just gone. Did I accidentally click something or did everyone decide that I suck?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-06T15:50:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u0027s an option that says \u0022don\u0027t allow others to follow me\u0022 right on that tab in the profile. Check it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbalsaurus","CreatedById":222386,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-06T16:17:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224356344\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022222685\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221704556242\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n25 minutes ago, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u0027s an option that says \u0022don\u0027t allow others to follow me\u0022 right on that tab in the profile. Check it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAllow others to follow me is on. Maybe I screwed something up in settings?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbart","CreatedById":78303,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-06T16:29:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022f